Mission Desc: Build a Pizzeria. Tip: Place your commerce close to houses to have more customers
Rename your City. Click on the HQ then click on the change name icon beside the name to change it. You can change you city name anytime in the game.
Click on a property under construction to do an Instant Build. Tip: Build a House and connect it to the HQ and then once the build timer is counting down click the House to confirm an Instant Build.
Build 2 Trees. Tip: Go to the Shop and select the Decorations tab. Buy a tree and place it next to a House to increase the House Bonus. Do it one more time.
Build more Houses around the Pizzeria to increase the customers to 10. Tip: Buy plots next to the Pizzeria. Go to the Shop and buy Houses and sign the contracts to get the Tenants.
Arrange a Pizzeria Sale event 5 times. Tip: Click the Pizzeria after the Timer has counted down 5 times.
Build a House. Tip: Buy a 2x2 plot with the Buy Plots tool. Go to the Shop and select the Bungalow Luxury and place it on the plot.
Wonders are great for big Bonuses. Build 1 Golden Statue. Tip: First place 4x4 plots then go to the Shop and select the Wonders tab. Click the Golden statue and place it in the empty plot.
Collect 10 rents from your Houses. Tip: Use shorter contracts to finish the Mission quickly
Get a total Company Value of $5M. Tip: Collect from shorter House contracts and commerce to quickly increase your cash flow.
